{"title":"Emmet的html语法","date":"2017-07-28T16:00:00.000Z","slug":"Emmet的html语法","comments":true,"tags":["html"],"updated":"2019-09-23T07:41:35.816Z","content":"<p>[TOC]</p>\n<p>所有操作按下“tab”键即可瞬间完成</p>\n<h2 id=\"元素\"><a href=\"#元素\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"元素\"></a>元素</h2><ol>\n<li>在编辑器中输入元素名称，即可自动补全生成 HTML 标签，即使不是标准的 HTML 标签。 </li>\n<li>输入：! 或者 html:5 或者 html:4s 或者 html:4t 将自动补全html基本结构</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"嵌套操作\"><a href=\"#嵌套操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"嵌套操作\"></a>嵌套操作</h2><h3 id=\"使用“-gt-”生成子元素\"><a href=\"#使用“-gt-”生成子元素\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用“&gt;”生成子元素\"></a>使用“&gt;”生成子元素</h3><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 输入</span><br><span class=\"line\">div&gt;ul&gt;li</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// 按下TAB键</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"使用“-”生成兄弟元素\"><a href=\"#使用“-”生成兄弟元素\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用“+”生成兄弟元素\"></a>使用“+”生成兄弟元素</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 输入</span><br><span class=\"line\">div+p+bq</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// 按下TAB键</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"使用“-”生成父元素\"><a href=\"#使用“-”生成父元素\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用“^”生成父元素\"></a>使用“^”生成父元素</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 输入</span><br><span class=\"line\">div+div&gt;p&gt;span+em^bq</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// 按下TAB键</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"使用“-”生成多个相同元素\"><a href=\"#使用“-”生成多个相同元素\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用“*”生成多个相同元素\"></a>使用“*”生成多个相同元素</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 输入</span><br><span class=\"line\">div&gt;ul&gt;li*5</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// 按下TAB键</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;ul&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;/ul&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"使用“-”将元素分组\"><a href=\"#使用“-”将元素分组\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用“()”将元素分组\"></a>使用“()”将元素分组</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 输入</span><br><span class=\"line\">// &quot;+&quot; 后面的元素与括号中的第一个元素属于兄弟关系</span><br><span class=\"line\">div&gt;(header&gt;ul&gt;li*2)+footer&gt;p</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">//按下TAB键</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;header&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;ul&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;/ul&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;/header&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;footer&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;/footer&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"属性操作\"><a href=\"#属性操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"属性操作\"></a>属性操作</h2><h3 id=\"id与class：元素与-id-属性值之间用-“-”-分隔，与-class-属性值之间用-“-”-分隔\"><a href=\"#id与class：元素与-id-属性值之间用-“-”-分隔，与-class-属性值之间用-“-”-分隔\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"id与class：元素与 id 属性值之间用 “#” 分隔，与 class 属性值之间用 “.” 分隔\"></a>id与class：元素与 id 属性值之间用 “#” 分隔，与 class 属性值之间用 “.” 分隔</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 输入</span><br><span class=\"line\">div#header+div.page+div#footer.class1.class2.class3</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// 按下TAB键</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;div id=&quot;header&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;div class=&quot;page&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;div id=&quot;footer&quot; class=&quot;class1 class2 class3&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"使用“-”标记其他属性\"><a href=\"#使用“-”标记其他属性\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用“[]”标记其他属性\"></a>使用“[]”标记其他属性</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 输入</span><br><span class=\"line\">td[title=&apos;hello&apos; colspan=3]</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// 按下TAB键</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;td title=&quot;hello&quot; colspan=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"用“-”符号实现1到n的自动编号（“-”实现多个元素）\"><a href=\"#用“-”符号实现1到n的自动编号（“-”实现多个元素）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"用“$”符号实现1到n的自动编号（“*”实现多个元素）\"></a>用“$”符号实现1到n的自动编号（“*”实现多个元素）</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 输入</span><br><span class=\"line\">li.item$*3</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// 按下TAB键</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;li class=&quot;item1&quot;&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;li class=&quot;item2&quot;&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;li class=&quot;item3&quot;&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"可在-“-”-后添加-“-n”-修改编号的起始值为n。\"><a href=\"#可在-“-”-后添加-“-n”-修改编号的起始值为n。\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"可在 “$” 后添加 “@n” 修改编号的起始值为n。\"></a>可在 “$” 后添加 “@n” 修改编号的起始值为n。</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 输入</span><br><span class=\"line\">li.item$@3*3</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// 按下TAB键</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;li class=&quot;item3&quot;&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;li class=&quot;item4&quot;&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;li class=&quot;item5&quot;&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"可在-“-”-后添加-“-”-修改编号的方向。\"><a href=\"#可在-“-”-后添加-“-”-修改编号的方向。\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"可在 “$” 后添加 “@-” 修改编号的方向。\"></a>可在 “$” 后添加 “@-” 修改编号的方向。</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 输入</span><br><span class=\"line\">li.item$@-3*3</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// 按下TAB键</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;li class=&quot;item5&quot;&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;li class=&quot;item4&quot;&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;li class=&quot;item3&quot;&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"用“-”添加文本内容\"><a href=\"#用“-”添加文本内容\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"用“{}”添加文本内容\"></a>用“{}”添加文本内容</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 输入</span><br><span class=\"line\">a[href=me.htm]&#123;click me&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// 按下TAB键</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;a href=&quot;me.htm&quot;&gt;click me&lt;/a&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"npm - 换淘宝源","slug":"npm - 换淘宝源"},"next":{"title":"notepad++ 正则表达式","slug":"notepad正则表达式"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/Emmet的html语法/","toc":[{"title":"元素","id":"元素","index":"1"},{"title":"嵌套操作","id":"嵌套操作","index":"2","children":[{"title":"使用“&gt;”生成子元素","id":"使用“-gt-”生成子元素","index":"2.1"},{"title":"使用“+”生成兄弟元素","id":"使用“-”生成兄弟元素","index":"2.2"},{"title":"使用“^”生成父元素","id":"使用“-”生成父元素","index":"2.3"},{"title":"使用“*”生成多个相同元素","id":"使用“-”生成多个相同元素","index":"2.4"},{"title":"使用“()”将元素分组","id":"使用“-”将元素分组","index":"2.5"}]},{"title":"属性操作","id":"属性操作","index":"3","children":[{"title":"id与class：元素与 id 属性值之间用 “#” 分隔，与 class 属性值之间用 “.” 分隔","id":"id与class：元素与-id-属性值之间用-“-”-分隔，与-class-属性值之间用-“-”-分隔","index":"3.1"},{"title":"使用“[]”标记其他属性","id":"使用“-”标记其他属性","index":"3.2"},{"title":"用“$”符号实现1到n的自动编号（“*”实现多个元素）","id":"用“-”符号实现1到n的自动编号（“-”实现多个元素）","index":"3.3"},{"title":"可在 “$” 后添加 “@n” 修改编号的起始值为n。","id":"可在-“-”-后添加-“-n”-修改编号的起始值为n。","index":"3.4"},{"title":"可在 “$” 后添加 “@-” 修改编号的方向。","id":"可在-“-”-后添加-“-”-修改编号的方向。","index":"3.5"},{"title":"用“{}”添加文本内容","id":"用“-”添加文本内容","index":"3.6"}]}]}